Specifically about guarantee
:SKRSLUT.
.in
.ir
.sp 2mm
.cd 2 5mm 90mm
.cl 78mm
.**1. KOLONNE *************************************************************
.tp 3mm
:FED.
1. Extent of guarantee
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The third party guarantor is held liable for debtors obligations
towards &BANKNAVN., including interest and other minor debt
services, to the extent that the total amount to be paid does not
exceed the principal amount of the loan or the credit limit on
placing the guarantee.
.sp 2mm
:FED.
2. Expiry :SKRSLUT.
.br
The guarantee expires after 10 years, however, after 5 years in case of
guarantee of credit with floating loan amount and loans without fixed
due date. The claim of &BANKNAVN. against the third party
guarantor does not expire if the claim is sustained prior to the
expiry of the guarantee.
.sp 2mm
:FED.
3. Reversal :SKRSLUT.
.br
If the loan/credit is repaid, fully or partly, and the payment or
additional security is set aside at a later point in time, the
guarantee will be maintained, whether you or &BANKNAVN. has
notified the third party guarantor of the repayment or not.
.sp 2mm
:FED.
4. Use of payments :SKRSLUT.
.br
Payments from third party guarantors are first of all used in settlement
of interest, commission and expenses, secondly in settlement of other
debt secured by the third party guarantor.
.sp 2mm
If the loan/credit is not fully secured by the guarantee, debtors
payments, or payments from others than the third party guarantor, are
first of all used in settlement of the unsecured part of the debt.
.sp 3mm
.of
.cb
.* 2. KOLONNE **************************
:FED.
5. Respite :SKRSLUT.
.br
Without consent of third party guarantor, &BANKNAVN. may grant a
respite as to payment of instalments, interest and other
expenses, however, with deference to article 48 of the Danish
Financial Business Act.
.sp 2mm
:FED.
6. Voting right at creditors' meetings :SKRSLUT.
.br
At any creditors' meeting regarding you, &BANKNAVN. will exercise the
voting right connected to the object of the guarantee. This applies until
&BANKNAVN. has obtained full and irrefutable settlement of its claims.
.sp 2mm
:FED.
7. Joint guaranties and other securities :SKRSLUT.
.br
&BANKNAVN. reserves its right to realise any securities applied by you or
third party and write off the revenue at the option of &BANKNAVN.. The
third party guarantor has no right of recourse.
.sp 2mm
This implies, among other things:
.of 3mm
* ¤ that &BANKNAVN., without the permission of the third party
guarantor, may release other securities in relation to the
obligation in question.
.of
.br
.of 3mm
* ¤ that &BANKNAVN. may use pledge/mortgage, which at the same time serves
as security against other claims but the obligation in question, in prior
recovery of such claims.
.of
.sp 2mm
.kp on
:FED.
8. Notification right and right to dividend upon debtors liquidation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
If the third party guarantor has to discharge debtors obligations towards
&BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. has notification right and right to dividend of the
amount paid in debtors estate.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
9. Enforcement :SKRSLUT.
.br
If the guarantee serves as security against loan, the loan instrument
with deed of indemnity may serve as basis for enforcement with the
third party guarantor according to article 478, section 1, paragraph
5 of the Danish Administration of Justice Act.
.kp off
.sc
.in 5mm
.ir 5mm

